<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd" >
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <title>${title}</title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <meta name="description" content="" />
        <meta name="author" content="" />
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="${asset:context:/favicon.ico}" />
    </head>
    
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <nav class="navbar navbar-default" role="navigation">
                    <a class="navbar-brand" t:type="pagelink" page="Index">MetHotels</a>
                    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbar-collapse-1">
                        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-left">
                            <t:loop source="leftNavigationMenu" value="navItem">
                                <t:if test="${!navItem.subPages}">
                                    <t:any element="li" class="prop:classForPageName">
                                        <t:pagelink page="${navItem.mainPage}">${getMenuPageName(navItem.mainPage)}</t:pagelink>
                                    </t:any>
                                </t:if>
                                <t:if test="${navItem.subPages}">
                                    <t:any element="li" class="dropdown prop:classForPageName">
                                        <t:pagelink data-toggle="dropdown" class="dropdown-toggle" page="${navItem.mainPage}">
                                            ${getMenuPageName(navItem.mainPage)}<b class="caret"></b>
                                        </t:pagelink>
                                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                            <t:loop source="navItem.subPages" value="var:subPage">
                                                <t:any element="li" class="prop:classForPageName">
                                                               <!-- 
                                                                Does not work: ${getMenuPageName(var:subPage)} 
                                                                might have to create property subPage
                                                                -->
                                                    <t:pagelink page="var:subPage">${var:subPage}</t:pagelink>
                                                </t:any>
                                            </t:loop>
                                        </ul>
                                    </t:any>
                                </t:if>
                            </t:loop>
                        </ul>
                        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                            <t:if test="!loggedIn">
                                <li><a t:type="pagelink" page="Prijava">Prijava</a></li>
                                <li>|</li>
                                <li><a t:type="pagelink" page="Registracija">Registracija</a> </li>
                            </t:if>
                            <t:if test="loggedIn">
                                <li><t:actionlink t:id="logout">Odjava</t:actionlink></li> 
                                <li>|</li>
                                <li>Welcome ${loggedInKorisnik.korisnickoIme}!</li>
                            </t:if>
                        </ul>

                    </div>
                </nav>
            </div>
            
            <t:if test="showBodyTitle">
                <h3 class="text-muted" style="text-align:center;">${title}</h3>
            </t:if>
            
            <t:body />
            
            <!-- <div class="standard_border"></div> -->
            
            <!-- include marketing content for some pages if needed -->
            <t:if test="showMarketing">
                <div class="standard_border"></div>
                
                <div class="row marketing">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <h4>Smestaj</h4>
                        <img src="images/apartments.jpg" alt=""></img>
                        <p>Hotel u svom sastavu ima luksuzno opremljene apartmane , premium sobe , superior sobe , standardne sobe , spa centar i restoran. Apartmani su...</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <h4>Spa centar</h4> 
                        <img src="images/croppedimage300140-spa2.JPG" alt=""></img>
                        <p>Danasnjica iziskuje psihofizicki napor i konstantan stres, ciji su uzroci brz tempo Divljenja i nedostatak vremena. Idealnu relaksaciju nasim...</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <h4>Restoran</h4>
                        <img src="images/croppedimage300140-rest1.JPG" alt="" ></img>
                        <p>Cafe restoran, svojim luksuznim stilom i udobnoscu, predstavlja idealno mesto sa uslugom radnog dorucka i slatkog predaha uz nase kolace. Bez...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </t:if>
            
            <footer class="footer">
                <p>&copy; Rile 2015</p>
            </footer>

        </div>
        <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    </body>
    
</html>
